<lyrics>[V1]
.C               G
 Iso Masih choʻponim,
.               C
 Mening shohim Xudovand,
.      Am      G     F
 Men muhtojlik koʻrmayman aslo,
.   Dm7    G    C
 Halleluya, Tasanno.

[V2]
.    F    G  C
 Iso Seni sevaman,
.    F   G      C
 Hamdu sano kuylayman,
.    Am   G     F
 Qanotingda uchaman Rabbim,
.      Dm7  G     C
 Yurakdan rahmat deyman.</lyrics>
<key>C</key>
<title>Iso Masih Choʻponim ҲСХМ156</title>
</song>